summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Stewart Street from the alley between 8th & 9th Avenues to Eastlake Avenue et al, in the City of Seattle, by paving same under Ordinance No. 19562, creating Local Improvement District No. 1894 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
